  <name>Webfont Kit Generator</name>
  <summary>Create @font-face kits easily</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Webfont Kit Generator is a simple utility that allows you to generate woff, woff2 and the necessary CSS boilerplate from non-web font formats (otf and ttf).
    </p>
    <p>
      Webfont Kit Generator uses fontTools python library under the hood.
    </p>
  </description>  
